message.content:
Tēnā rawa atu, ka āwhina ahau ki te whakawhanake i tētahi hātepe e taea ai te whakakore i ngā kupuhipa me ētahi atu tikanga haumaru. Kia taea e koe te whakamahi i te reo Māori ki te whakamāramatanga i ēnei whakaritenga. 

1. Whakapā atu ki te rōpū whakahaere o te rorohiko: 
   Me whakapā atu koe ki tō rōpū whakahaere o te rorohiko, ki te rapu i ētahi hōtaka whakakore kupuhipa. Ka whakaae rātou ki te āwhina i a koe ki te whakakore i ngā kupuhipa.

2. Whakatikatika i tō rorohiko: 
   Me whakapai i tō rorohiko ki te whakahaere i ētahi whakahōputu, whakapau kaha hoki. Me whakapai hoki i ngā whakaputanga o te rorohiko me ngā whakahōputu hei whakakore i ngā kupuhipa.

3. Tīmata i te hōtaka whakakore kupuhipa: 
   Whakaritea tētahi wā e whakakore ai i ngā kupuhipa. Tīmata i te hōtaka whakakore kupuhipa i te wā e whakapau kaha ana te rorohiko.

4. Aroturuki i ngā whakahōputu: 
   Me aroturuki i ngā whakahōputu i te taha o te rorohiko hei whakakore i ngā kupuhipa. Tirohia ngā kupu e whakaae ana ko ngā kupuhipa, ā, whakakorehia ēnei kupu.

5. Whakapau kaha i te hōtaka whakakore
